flowchart TD
  A[User opens task detail from board, inbox, overview, or deep link] --> B[Load GET /tasks/:taskId/detail]
  B --> C[Read browser session roles and permissions]
  C --> D[Resolve task signals: stage, owner, blocked state, waiting state, freshness, monitoring, close governance]
  D --> E{Role and state require action?}
  E -->|PM refinement or assignment| PM[Show PM next-action panel with owner/refinement shortcut]
  E -->|Architect or engineer handoff| ENG[Show delivery handoff shortcut and evidence expectations]
  E -->|QA verification| QA[Show QA result action and evidence requirements]
  E -->|SRE monitoring| SRE[Show monitoring state, expiry, approval or blocking reason]
  E -->|Human decision| H[Show decision cluster and close-review context]
  E -->|Reader or missing permission| R[Show status-only panel without edit controls]
  E -->|No immediate action| P[Show passive monitoring, owner, freshness, history, and telemetry paths]
  PM --> F[User follows anchor or existing control]
  ENG --> F
  QA --> F
  SRE --> F
  H --> F
  R --> G[Audit, telemetry, comments, and history remain inspectable when permitted]
  P --> G
  F --> I[Existing mutation endpoint records workflow event]
  I --> J[Projection refresh updates task detail read model]
  J --> D
  F --> M[Emit sanitized action-click metric]
  D --> N[Emit sanitized action-impression metric]
